{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>Snapshot Spirit Live!</i> you play as a jetpack-flying photographer named Katie as she hunts ghosts in this educational photography game with minimalist 1-bit-inspired graphics and a Game Boy-inspired soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351100/extras/sslpromoscreenshots__19_.png?t=1738695290\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Katie as she flies around a haunted forest to find and photograph a wide variety of cute ghosts and build her photo portfolio. Katie streams her photography and jetpack-flying adventures to viewers, and she comments on what happens each day!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351100/extras/allfeatures__2_.png?t=1738695290\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As she gets better at photography, more and more camera features unlock, allowing players to learn about basic photography principles such as the exposure triangle, ISO, aperture, shutter speed, and focus.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351100/extras/sslpromoscreenshots__29_.png?t=1738695290\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738695290","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351100/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738695290","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351100/dfda77788999b2df32af5cabadb2e25349312ccd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738695290","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351100/dfda77788999b2df32af5cabadb2e25349312ccd/capsule_184